legacy.name: Hua Chunying 华春莹

legacy.full_text: We call on the relevant parties to immediately act on the UN resolution, respect international law, especially international humanitarian law, cease hostilities, and seek solutions that will lead to the peaceful coexistence of Palestinians and Israelis. (4/4)

legacy.description:
Assistant Minister of Foreign Affairs, 
Foreign Ministry Spokesperson, 
Director General, Information Department, MFA PRC. 
Get to know us more @MFA_China
legacy.name: Hua Chunying 华春莹

legacy.full_text: Retaliations will only result in more deaths & hatred and end up in a vicious cycle of violence-for-violence. Sustainable security can only be attained on the basis of common security. International fairness & justice can only be upheld by observing international law.  (3/4)

Foreign Ministry Spokesperson, 
Director General, Information Department, MFA PRC. 
Get to know us more @MFA_China
legacy.name: Hua Chunying 华春莹

legacy.full_text: We condemn all acts that harm & endanger civilians. All lives are precious. The life of Palestinians, like that of all other peoples, must be protected. If history is any guide, violence cannot bring durable peace. (2/4)
